ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNCcXQ2WlJ3EAE,ChIJY7ekJ7upQjQRD-WjBStDYh4,5,"I highly recommend it.
為 150, I had 10 dumplings (pork and cabbage), seasoned cucumber, and braised egg.

The menu isn't extensive, so you can use Papago Translate or BigSub Vision to translate the menu and order.

Locals tend to order a lot of soup, but we weren't able to try it because we lacked the courage.

The waitress was friendly and spoke a little English.

You might have to wait in line for a bit, but the turnover is fast.

While you wait, you can watch other people eat and get an idea of​​ what to order.

You can order dumplings in multiples of 10, 15, or 20.

If you want a mix of pork and cabbage dumplings and chive dumplings, you can order from 20 or more.

Highly recommended!

When you enter the market, turn right at the first intersection and keep going. 你會看到的。",5,5,5
